{
  "version": "Notebook/1.0",
  "items": [
    {
      "type": 1,
      "content": {
        "json": "# AVS Metrics Workbook (No Log Analytics Required)\r\n\r\nThis workbook uses **only free data sources**: Azure Resource Graph, the Azure Monitor metrics API (93-day platform metric retention), and Azure Alerts Management. No Log Analytics Workspace is required and no diagnostic settings need to be configured.\r\n\r\n**Data sources used:**\r\n- Azure Resource Graph (free) — inventory, SKU, host counts, networking, datastores\r\n- Azure Monitor platform metrics (free, 93-day retention) — CPU, memory, vSAN, datastore charts\r\n- Azure Alerts Management (free) — active alerts on AVS resources\r\n\r\n**Limitations vs. LAW-based workbooks:** no syslog visibility, no NSX firewall logs, no log-search alerts, single charts capped at 30 days (data still retained 93 days, just pan the time picker)."
      },
      "name": "text - intro"
    },
    {
      "type": 9,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "id": "p-timerange",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "TimeRange",
            "type": 4,
            "isRequired": true,
            "value": {
              "durationMs": 86400000
            },
            "typeSettings": {
              "selectableValues": [
                { "durationMs": 3600000 },
                { "durationMs": 14400000 },
                { "durationMs": 43200000 },
                { "durationMs": 86400000 },
                { "durationMs": 172800000 },
                { "durationMs": 604800000 },
                { "durationMs": 2592000000 }
              ],
              "allowCustom": true
            }
          },
          {
            "id": "p-subscription",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "Subscription",
            "type": 6,
            "isRequired": true,
            "multiSelect": true,
            "quote": "'",
            "delimiter": ",",
            "query": "where type =~ 'microsoft.avs/privateclouds'\r\n| summarize Count = count() by subscriptionId\r\n| order by Count desc\r\n| project value = subscriptionId, label = subscriptionId, selected = true",
            "crossComponentResources": [ "value::all" ],
            "typeSettings": {
              "additionalResourceOptions": [ "value::all" ],
              "showDefault": false
            },
            "queryType": 1,
            "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources",
            "value": [ "value::all" ]
          },
          {
            "id": "p-avsinstance",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "AVSInstance",
            "label": "AVS Instance",
            "type": 5,
            "isRequired": true,
            "multiSelect": true,
            "quote": "'",
            "delimiter": ",",
            "query": "resources\r\n| where type =~ 'microsoft.avs/privateclouds'\r\n| project value = id, label = name",
            "crossComponentResources": [ "{Subscription}" ],
            "typeSettings": {
              "additionalResourceOptions": [ "value::all" ],
              "showDefault": false
            },
            "queryType": 1,
            "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources",
            "value": [ "value::all" ]
          }
        ],
        "style": "pills",
        "queryType": 1,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources"
      },
      "name": "parameters"
    },
    {
      "type": 11,
      "content": {
        "version": "LinkItem/1.0",
        "style": "tabs",
        "links": [
          { "id": "tab-overview", "cellValue": "Tab", "linkTarget": "parameter", "linkLabel": "Overview", "subTarget": "Overview", "style": "link" },
          { "id": "tab-performance", "cellValue": "Tab", "linkTarget": "parameter", "linkLabel": "Performance", "subTarget": "Performance", "style": "link" },
          { "id": "tab-storage", "cellValue": "Tab", "linkTarget": "parameter", "linkLabel": "Storage", "subTarget": "Storage", "style": "link" },
          { "id": "tab-capacity", "cellValue": "Tab", "linkTarget": "parameter", "linkLabel": "Capacity & Inventory", "subTarget": "Capacity", "style": "link" },
          { "id": "tab-alerts", "cellValue": "Tab", "linkTarget": "parameter", "linkLabel": "Alerts", "subTarget": "Alerts", "style": "link" }
        ]
      },
      "name": "tabs"
    },
    {
      "type": 12,
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "## Overview\r\nAt-a-glance health of your AVS estate. All data sourced from Azure Resource Graph and Alerts Management (free)."
            },
            "name": "text - overview-header"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "resources\r\n| where type =~ 'microsoft.avs/privateclouds'\r\n| where id in ({AVSInstance})\r\n| count\r\n| project Label = 'Private Clouds', Value = Count",
              "size": 4,
              "title": "Private Clouds",
              "queryType": 1,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources",
              "crossComponentResources": [ "{Subscription}" ],
              "visualization": "tiles",
              "tileSettings": {
                "showBorder": false,
                "titleContent": { "columnMatch": "Label", "formatter": 1 },
                "leftContent": { "columnMatch": "Value", "formatter": 12, "formatOptions": { "palette": "blue" } }
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "25",
            "name": "kpi-pcs"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "resources\r\n| where type =~ 'microsoft.avs/privateclouds/clusters' or (type =~ 'microsoft.avs/privateclouds' and id in ({AVSInstance}))\r\n| extend clusterSize = iff(type =~ 'microsoft.avs/privateclouds', toint(properties.managementCluster.clusterSize), toint(properties.clusterSize))\r\n| summarize TotalHosts = sum(clusterSize)\r\n| project Label = 'Hosts', Value = TotalHosts",
              "size": 4,
              "title": "Total Hosts",
              "queryType": 1,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources",
              "crossComponentResources": [ "{Subscription}" ],
              "visualization": "tiles",
              "tileSettings": {
                "showBorder": false,
                "titleContent": { "columnMatch": "Label", "formatter": 1 },
                "leftContent": { "columnMatch": "Value", "formatter": 12, "formatOptions": { "palette": "green" } }
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "25",
            "name": "kpi-hosts"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "resources\r\n| where type =~ 'microsoft.avs/privateclouds/clusters' or (type =~ 'microsoft.avs/privateclouds' and id in ({AVSInstance}))\r\n| count\r\n| project Label = 'Clusters', Value = Count",
              "size": 4,
              "title": "Total Clusters",
              "queryType": 1,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources",
              "crossComponentResources": [ "{Subscription}" ],
              "visualization": "tiles",
              "tileSettings": {
                "showBorder": false,
                "titleContent": { "columnMatch": "Label", "formatter": 1 },
                "leftContent": { "columnMatch": "Value", "formatter": 12, "formatOptions": { "palette": "purple" } }
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "25",
            "name": "kpi-clusters"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "alertsmanagementresources\r\n| where type =~ 'microsoft.alertsmanagement/alerts'\r\n| where properties.essentials.targetResourceType =~ 'microsoft.avs/privateclouds'\r\n| where properties.essentials.alertState in~ ('New', 'Acknowledged')\r\n| count\r\n| project Label = 'Active Alerts', Value = Count",
              "size": 4,
              "title": "Active Alerts",
              "queryType": 1,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources",
              "crossComponentResources": [ "{Subscription}" ],
              "visualization": "tiles",
              "tileSettings": {
                "showBorder": false,
                "titleContent": { "columnMatch": "Label", "formatter": 1 },
                "leftContent": { "columnMatch": "Value", "formatter": 12, "formatOptions": { "palette": "redBright" } }
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "25",
            "name": "kpi-alerts"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "resources\r\n| where type =~ 'microsoft.avs/privateclouds'\r\n| where id in ({AVSInstance})\r\n| extend provisioningState = tostring(properties.provisioningState)\r\n| extend internet = tostring(properties.internet)\r\n| extend skuName = tostring(sku.name)\r\n| extend clusterSize = toint(properties.managementCluster.clusterSize)\r\n| extend hasCircuit = iff(isnotempty(tostring(properties.circuit.expressRoutePrivatePeeringId)), 'Connected', 'Not Connected')\r\n| project name, resourceGroup, location, provisioningState, skuName, clusterSize, internet, hasCircuit",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Private Cloud Health Status",
              "noDataMessage": "No AVS Private Clouds found in selected subscription(s)",
              "showExportToExcel": true,
              "queryType": 1,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources",
              "crossComponentResources": [ "{Subscription}" ],
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "provisioningState",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "icons",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        { "operator": "==", "thresholdValue": "Succeeded", "representation": "success", "text": "{0}{1}" },
                        { "operator": "==", "thresholdValue": "Failed", "representation": "3", "text": "{0}{1}" },
                        { "operator": "Default", "thresholdValue": null, "representation": "warning", "text": "{0}{1}" }
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "internet",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "icons",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        { "operator": "==", "thresholdValue": "Enabled", "representation": "success", "text": "{0}{1}" },
                        { "operator": "Default", "thresholdValue": null, "representation": "disabled", "text": "{0}{1}" }
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "hasCircuit",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "icons",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        { "operator": "==", "thresholdValue": "Connected", "representation": "success", "text": "{0}{1}" },
                        { "operator": "Default", "thresholdValue": null, "representation": "warning", "text": "{0}{1}" }
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  { "columnMatch": "clusterSize", "formatter": 4, "formatOptions": { "palette": "blue" } }
                ],
                "filter": true,
                "labelSettings": [
                  { "columnId": "name", "label": "Private Cloud" },
                  { "columnId": "resourceGroup", "label": "Resource Group" },
                  { "columnId": "location", "label": "Location" },
                  { "columnId": "provisioningState", "label": "Status" },
                  { "columnId": "skuName", "label": "SKU" },
                  { "columnId": "clusterSize", "label": "Hosts" },
                  { "columnId": "internet", "label": "Internet" },
                  { "columnId": "hasCircuit", "label": "ExpressRoute" }
                ]
              }
            },
            "name": "table-health"
          },
          {
            "type": 10,
            "content": {
              "chartId": "ovw-cpu-trend",
              "version": "MetricsItem/2.0",
              "size": 0,
              "chartType": 2,
              "resourceType": "Microsoft.AVS/privateClouds",
              "metricScope": 0,
              "resourceParameter": "AVSInstance",
              "resourceIds": [ "{AVSInstance}" ],
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "timeContext": { "durationMs": 86400000 },
              "metrics": [
                {
                  "namespace": "microsoft.avs/privateclouds",
                  "metric": "microsoft.avs/privateclouds--CpuUsageAverage",
                  "aggregation": 4,
                  "splitBy": [ "clustername" ]
                }
              ],
              "title": "CPU Utilization (%) by Cluster",
              "showRefreshButton": true
            },
            "customWidth": "50",
            "name": "metric-cpu"
          },
          {
            "type": 10,
            "content": {
              "chartId": "ovw-mem-trend",
              "version": "MetricsItem/2.0",
              "size": 0,
              "chartType": 2,
              "resourceType": "Microsoft.AVS/privateClouds",
              "metricScope": 0,
              "resourceParameter": "AVSInstance",
              "resourceIds": [ "{AVSInstance}" ],
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "timeContext": { "durationMs": 86400000 },
              "metrics": [
                {
                  "namespace": "microsoft.avs/privateclouds",
                  "metric": "microsoft.avs/privateclouds--MemUsageAverage",
                  "aggregation": 4,
                  "splitBy": [ "clustername" ]
                }
              ],
              "title": "Memory Utilization (%) by Cluster",
              "showRefreshButton": true
            },
            "customWidth": "50",
            "name": "metric-mem"
          },
          {
            "type": 10,
            "content": {
              "chartId": "ovw-vsan",
              "version": "MetricsItem/2.0",
              "size": 0,
              "chartType": 2,
              "resourceType": "Microsoft.AVS/privateClouds",
              "metricScope": 0,
              "resourceParameter": "AVSInstance",
              "resourceIds": [ "{AVSInstance}" ],
              "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
              "timeContext": { "durationMs": 86400000 },
              "metrics": [
                {
                  "namespace": "microsoft.avs/privateclouds",
                  "metric": "microsoft.avs/privateclouds--DiskUsedPercentage",
                  "aggregation": 4,
                  "splitBy": [ "dsname" ]
                }
              ],
              "title": "vSAN Datastore Used (%) by Datastore",
              "showRefreshButton": true
            },
            "name": "metric-vsan"
          }
        ]
      },
      "conditionalVisibility": { "parameterName": "Tab", "comparison": "isEqualTo", "value": "Overview" },
      "name": "group-overview"
    },
    {
      "type": 12,
      "content": {
